com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.constants

Class Style

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.constants.Style

  • public class Style
extends Object

    Style provides URLs to several professional styles designed by Mapbox.

    These styles are all ready to go in your app. To load one, pass it into MapView.setStyleUrl(String)
    See Also:
    MapView.setStyleUrl(String)
